
/* Sticky header for Genesis Sample Theme */

.site-header {
    position: fixed;
    width: 100%;
    z-index: 1000;
}

nav.nav-primary {
    padding-top: 164px; /*height of header (can be easily obtained using Firebug or another web browser developer tool)*/
}
The above is a generic site-wide solution.

In this particular demo, the actual CSS used to restrict to just this Page is:

/* Sticky header */

.page-id-236 .site-header {
    position: fixed;
    width: 100%;
    z-index: 1000;
}

.page-id-236 nav.nav-primary {
    padding-top: 164px; /*height of header (can be easily obtained using Firebug)*/
}
